te><blockquote>洗唔洗交相</blockquote><br />\n交相係for學生證</blockquote><br />\n幾時先要交?可唔可以上網交"},{"pid":"0232266d8736852a03b6a517872159d9aa00c6a6","tid":350811,"uid":134120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗交相</blockquote><br />\n交相係for學生證</blockquote><br />\n幾時先要交?可唔可以上網交</blockquote><br />\n你要留意返學校既email呀 我都唔記得我當年係點交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n穩陣起見就你去註冊既時候帶埋相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cf39d1f1342700d629d732d5d303850fb1dbf3","tid":350811,"uid":40751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:20:40.000Z","msg":"點睇電子及電腦工程學榮譽工學士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04baea692d74c7d6b0c159fd78319a64e966aac1","tid":350811,"uid":134134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>洗唔洗交相</blockquote><br />\n交相係for學生證</blockquote><br />\n幾時先要交?可唔可以上網交</blockquote><br />\n我係上網交嘅。我記得係去返myouhk(學生睇返啲學習資訊都係呢度)交。"},{"pid":"8281b20cae49d5061b0f1f9a1ff9ad3ab39920e9","tid":350811,"uid":89121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"如果簡錯科 有冇得year 2個陣轉科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同埋psycho係咪真係冇乜人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 想psycho轉nursing  黎緊year1"},{"pid":"fc8a861e92b0685d9bf3a6810fc9f6974ac7b47c","tid":350811,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:11:43.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇上莊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOu啲莊點"},{"pid":"2e63d2a440092100f5d0fac6913a66fe62